{"id":164293,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/杨紫琼因扮演昂山素季被缅甸驱逐/","date":"2011-06-28T09:30:03Z","modified":"2011-06-28T09:30:03Z","title":"杨紫琼因扮演昂山素季被缅甸驱逐","content":"<p>《联合早报》引用法新社报道称，缅甸将在电影《The Lady》中饰演昂山素季一角的杨紫琼递解出境，并将她列入黑名单，禁止再进入缅甸。缅甸官员表示，当杨紫琼抵达仰光国际机场时，被当局阻止入境，并递解出境。《The Lady》由法国导演洛比桑执导，在泰国拍摄，预计在今年稍后推出。 昂山素季是缅甸全国民主联盟的创办人、1990年诺贝尔和平奖得主，被缅甸当局软禁了15年，去年11月刚刚获释。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/163b10fa/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E6%9D%A8%E7%B4%AB%E7%90%BC%E5%9B%A0%E6%89%AE%E6%BC%94%E6%98%82%E5%B1%B1%E7%B4%A0%E5%AD%A3%E8%A2%AB%E7%BC%85%E7%94%B8%E9%A9%B1%E9%80%90&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F06%2F28%2F0348232%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%9D%A8%E7%B4%AB%E7%90%BC%E5%9B%A0%E6%89%AE%E6%BC%94%E6%98%82%E5%B1%B1%E7%B4%A0%E5%AD%A3%E8%A2%AB%E7%BC%85%E7%94%B8%E9%A9%B1%E9%80%90&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F06%2F28%2F0348232%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/106216000078/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/163b10fa/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/106216000078/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/163b10fa/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=cT9hLMxdRg8:84nm4aFhsH4:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=cT9hLMxdRg8:84nm4aFhsH4:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<